text: Entronque de Herradura is a village in the western province of Pinar del Río, Cuba. It is one of the 13 villages of the municipality Consolación del Sur. It covers 59.84 km². It was founded in 1907. == Other websites == Category:Settlements in Cuba Category:Villages in North America Category:1907 establishments in North America Category:20th-century establishments in Cuba
